message.entry: The initial delay should be a positive real number.
The delay step should be a non-negative real number.
The minimum delay, maximum delay and delay step should be non-negative real numbers.
The maximum delay should be greater than minimum delay plus delay step.
EbN0 should be a real number.
Frequency offset should be a real number.
Frequency resolution should be a real, positive scalar.
The normalized loop bandwidth of fine frequency compensation PLL should be a positive real number.
The damping factor of fine frequency compensation PLL should be a positive real number.
The normalized loop bandwidth of timing recovery PLL should be a positive real number.
The damping factor of timing recovery PLL should be a positive real number.
